The paper proposes a new framework for online learning with multiple kernels, specifically for classification tasks. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method also involves sparse learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the scalability of the proposed algorithm, which is relevant to systems and control (cs.SY).
